1:<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en"><head><meta charSet="utf-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/><link rel="stylesheet" href="/_next/static/css/395c85722f757a43.css" data-precedence="next"/><link rel="stylesheet" href="/_next/static/css/d22b38d7cb18f65e.css" data-precedence="next"/><link rel="preload" as="script" fetchPriority="low" href="/_next/static/chunks/webpack-82c1de09ba1b127f.js"/><script src="/_next/static/chunks/debe8953-0bd1ba602797935e.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/529-1ab94b75cf428a5f.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/main-app-f3b81acac6c88e32.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/993-561f2a040f3fc918.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/app/landing-exp/page-e0000b8b42eae432.js" async=""></script><meta name="next-size-adjust" content=""/><title>MUSU Early Access</title><meta name="description" content="Join MUSU early access to run a coordinated team of AI agents across your own machines."/><script src="/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js" noModule=""></script></head><body><div hidden=""><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class="page_page__C03nk __variable_c8daab __variable_75787b"><header class="page_topBar__Pxfhr"><a class="page_brand__X2iQ7 __className_75787b" href="/">MUSU</a><nav class="page_nav__lWfjX" aria-label="Primary"><a class="page_navLink__272Sl" href="/pricing">Pricing</a><a class="page_navLink__272Sl" href="/install">Install</a><a class="page_navLink__272Sl" href="/faq">FAQ</a><a class="page_navButton__8mjrN" href="/app">Open App</a></nav></header><main class="page_main__VrWto"><section class="page_hero__HUXS_" aria-labelledby="hero-title"><div class="page_heroCopy__1_sRm"><p class="page_eyebrow__EXYoZ">MUSU · THE AGENT RUNTIME FOR VIBE CODERS</p><h1 id="hero-title" class="page_heroTitle__o0_sj __className_75787b">Run a team of AIs across your own computers.</h1><p class="page_heroLead__LEDDV">One control plane. Chat or CLI. The work gets done without coordination drag.</p><div class="page_chipRow__jil9N"><span class="page_chip__vuFXM">solo developer with 2-3 machines</span><span class="page_chip__vuFXM">technical founder with a GPU box</span><span class="page_chip__vuFXM">operator who is tired of DIY orchestration</span></div><form class="page_waitlistForm__tR_2V" action="/api/waitlist?from=/landing-exp" method="post"><label for="waitlist-email" class="page_hiddenLabel__8GnJn">Waitlist email</label><input id="waitlist-email" type="email" required="" placeholder="you@company.com" autoComplete="email" class="page_waitlistInput__I4s4K" name="email"/><button type="submit" class="page_primaryCta__31P_Q __className_75787b">Try MUSU Early Access</button><a class="page_secondaryCta__cbooh" href="#how-it-works">Watch 90-sec demo</a></form><ul class="page_benefitList__VdGzr"><li class="page_benefitItem__ujMZa">Priority onboarding once access is ready</li><li class="page_benefitItem__ujMZa">Input into the product direction for multi-machine workflows</li><li class="page_benefitItem__ujMZa">Early visibility into pricing and plan changes</li></ul></div><div class="page_heroVisual__MUrHz"><div class="page_runtimeBoard__aIJJN"><div class="page_runtimeHeader__izcIV"><span class="page_runtimeTitle__ehL8o">Live Runtime Snapshot</span><span class="page_runtimeMeta__Xcsdc">control.musu</span></div><ul class="page_runtimeRows__emDxY"><li class="page_runtimeRow__yMZNi"><div><p class="page_runtimeHost__OcedR">4060Ti Builder Node</p><p class="page_runtimeDuty__siSVR">Patch generation + test loops</p></div><span class="page_statePill__YW7W0 page_stateReady__IlRoS">ready</span></li><li class="page_runtimeRow__yMZNi"><div><p class="page_runtimeHost__OcedR">5070Ti Dispatch Node</p><p class="page_runtimeDuty__siSVR">Long-context planning + orchestration</p></div><span class="page_statePill__YW7W0 page_stateBusy__N1_kK">busy</span></li><li class="page_runtimeRow__yMZNi"><div><p class="page_runtimeHost__OcedR">Laptop Operator Node</p><p class="page_runtimeDuty__siSVR">QA replay + release evidence</p></div><span class="page_statePill__YW7W0 page_stateReady__IlRoS">ready</span></li></ul><code class="page_commandRow__RQEyn">$ musu route --packet MUS-1636 --target 5070ti</code></div><div class="page_heroAside__JE9Ee"><p class="page_asideLabel__zT8hJ">Meaningful defaults</p><h2 class="page_asideTitle__P93rP __className_75787b">Ship over deliberate, never reckless.</h2><p class="page_asideBody__auqjS">MUSU prioritizes safe autonomy: fast where possible, gated where needed.</p></div></div></section><section class="page_referenceStrip__WuOH2" aria-label="Reference signals"><span class="page_referenceLead__MvSkM">Reference signals analyzed</span><div class="page_referenceList__e_gLS"><span class="page_referenceChip__CZb_L">Slack</span><span class="page_referenceChip__CZb_L">Front</span><span class="page_referenceChip__CZb_L">Missive</span><span class="page_referenceChip__CZb_L">Linear</span></div></section><section class="page_sectionBlock__GAUgy"><header class="page_sectionHeader__U9C8x"><p class="page_sectionEyebrow__y3Vxy">Problem to solution</p><h2 class="page_sectionTitle___eXSQ __className_75787b">Multi-machine operations should feel like one focused team.</h2></header><div class="page_cardGrid__NMS4X"><article class="page_infoCard__qs2au"><h3 class="page_infoTitle__f5Hgn __className_75787b">Coordination tax</h3><p class="page_infoBody__Gy0yh">Stop jumping between terminals, issue boards, and shell sessions to keep one lane moving.</p></article><article class="page_infoCard__qs2au"><h3 class="page_infoTitle__f5Hgn __className_75787b">Permission drag</h3><p class="page_infoBody__Gy0yh">Safe defaults keep destructive operations gated while normal execution stays fast.</p></article><article class="page_infoCard__qs2au"><h3 class="page_infoTitle__f5Hgn __className_75787b">Proof gaps</h3><p class="page_infoBody__Gy0yh">Every packet keeps owner, acceptance, and evidence in one control surface.</p></article></div></section><section id="how-it-works" class="page_sectionBlock__GAUgy"><header class="page_sectionHeader__U9C8x"><p class="page_sectionEyebrow__y3Vxy">How it works</p><h2 class="page_sectionTitle___eXSQ __className_75787b">Computers as departments. Agents as accountable operators.</h2></header><div class="page_installGrid__ynNxd"><article class="page_installCard__EUmWn"><p class="page_installPlatform__eY56X">Windows</p><h3 class="page_installTitle__kB2rl __className_75787b">Early-access onboarding</h3><p class="page_installStatus__S0u15">guided setup</p><p class="page_installBody__Ng28Z">Installer delivery is handled during onboarding while the public bootstrap endpoint is still being hardened.</p></article><article class="page_installCard__EUmWn"><p class="page_installPlatform__eY56X">Linux</p><h3 class="page_installTitle__kB2rl __className_75787b">Early-access onboarding</h3><p class="page_installStatus__S0u15">guided setup</p><p class="page_installBody__Ng28Z">Linux install instructions are issued after access approval so the public site does not point to a bootstrap URL that is not live yet.</p></article><article class="page_installCard__EUmWn"><p class="page_installPlatform__eY56X">macOS</p><h3 class="page_installTitle__kB2rl __className_75787b">Early-access onboarding</h3><p class="page_installStatus__S0u15">guided setup</p><p class="page_installBody__Ng28Z">macOS follows the same beta flow: confirm access, receive the install package, then connect the machine.</p></article></div></section><section class="page_sectionBlock__GAUgy"><header class="page_sectionHeader__U9C8x"><p class="page_sectionEyebrow__y3Vxy">Core surfaces</p><h2 class="page_sectionTitle___eXSQ __className_75787b">Operate from CLI when deep, switch to web when coordinating.</h2></header><div class="page_surfaceGrid__zti7Z"><article class="page_surfaceCard__QDoEk"><p class="page_surfaceMetric__u5gaJ">Low-latency control</p><h3 class="page_surfaceTitle__qINy8 __className_75787b">CLI + MCP is primary</h3><p class="page_surfaceBody__zAO4v">Route work, invoke agents, and read proof artifacts without leaving your operating context.</p></article><article class="page_surfaceCard__QDoEk"><p class="page_surfaceMetric__u5gaJ">Executive visibility</p><h3 class="page_surfaceTitle__qINy8 __className_75787b">Web GUI keeps status visible</h3><p class="page_surfaceBody__zAO4v">Observe queue health, packet ownership, and blockers in real time when you are away from terminal view.</p></article></div></section><section class="page_safetyBlock__EfeIT"><div><p class="page_sectionEyebrow__y3Vxy">Safety and autonomy</p><h2 class="page_sectionTitle___eXSQ __className_75787b">Autonomy where safe. Deliberation where it matters.</h2></div><ul class="page_safetyList__Tv1Qw"><li class="page_safetyItem__teSnw">Destructive operations require explicit approval paths.</li><li class="page_safetyItem__teSnw">Agent packets are rejected when acceptance criteria are weak.</li><li class="page_safetyItem__teSnw">Proof-first execution: no evidence, no completion.</li></ul></section><section class="page_finalCta__iW5cM"><h2 class="page_finalTitle__BxZ4L __className_75787b">Coordinate your AI workforce before scale becomes chaos.</h2><div class="page_finalActions__ZHwkf"><a class="page_primaryCta__31P_Q page_primaryCtaLink__dv6Xo __className_75787b" href="/landing">Join early access</a><a class="page_secondaryCta__cbooh" href="/install">Review install shape</a></div></section></main></div><!--$--><!--/$--><script src="/_next/static/chunks/webpack-82c1de09ba1b127f.js" id="_R_" async=""></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"1:\"$Sreact.fragment\"\n2:I[1144,[],\"\"]\n3:I[6686,[],\"\"]\n5:I[5813,[],\"OutletBoundary\"]\n7:I[8128,[],\"AsyncMetadataOutlet\"]\n9:I[5813,[],\"ViewportBoundary\"]\nb:I[5813,[],\"MetadataBoundary\"]\nc:\"$Sreact.suspense\"\ne:I[6756,[],\"\"]\nf:I[9993,[\"993\",\"static/chunks/9